From 7dba6995c1859bcec5d81e3082a0e80adead5e7f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 16:15:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Fix 48 audit findings: CRITICAL date parsing, auth, XSS,
 regulatory accuracy

CRITICAL fixes (7):
- compliance-suite.js: Fix SLA breach counter (slahours -> slaHours)
- compliance-suite.js: Fix CNMR/PNMR overdue detection (parseDDMMYYYY)
- compliance-suite.js: Fix retention expiry tracking (parseDDMMYYYY)
- report-generator.js: Replace forbidden FDL No.20/2018 with No.10/2025
- auth-rbac.js: Remove hardcoded 'admin123' password
- All Netlify functions: Wire authenticate() + rateLimit() middleware
- compliance-engine.mts: Fix fake token validation

HIGH fixes (17):
- supply-chain.js: Sync FATF Grey List (6 country fixes) with constants.ts
- supply-chain.js: Sync EU High-Risk List (14 country fixes) with constants.ts
- compliance-suite.js: Fix UBO review date parsing (parseDDMMYYYY)
- compliance-suite.js: Fix retention default 5->10 years
- compliance-suite.js: Fix red flag text "5-year" -> "10-year" retention
- compliance-suite.js: Fix XSS in country risk modal (esc())
- compliance-engine.mts: Restrict CORS to deployment origin
- get-file.mts: Add path traversal protection
- goaml-export.js: Add missing CNMR report type
- workflow-engine.js: Fix condition evaluator for non-field conditions
- workflow-engine.js: Fix async/await in runScan() and runDigest()
- src/App.tsx: Add React error boundary
- src/risk/decisions.ts: Null guard on redFlagScores
- src/risk/pfMonitoring.ts: Check originCountry for PF screening
- asana-readback-poller.js: Add pagination for >100 tasks
- tfs-refresh.js: Add audit trail on clearResults()

MEDIUM fixes (16):
- threshold-monitor.js: Use constants bridge (AED, USD, structuring)
- regulatory-monitor.js: Fix penalty cap AED 50M->100M, retention 5->10yr
- compliance-suite.js: Fix UID collision (add random suffix)
- compliance-suite.js: Escape badge() and badge2() status values
- compliance-engine.mts: Fix query param override, generic error messages
- mobile-responsive.js: Fix scroll lock + duplicate listener guard
- analytics-dashboard.js: Fix trend indicator color inversion
- workflow-engine.js: Business day calculator note
